00:41:46,490 --> 00:41:49,000
 Daddy, if she ran off with somebody--

929
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:50,030
 Now, don't worry, honey.

930
00:41:50,030 --> 00:41:50,930
Don't worry.

931
00:41:50,930 --> 00:41:52,970
She's not going to ruin your plans.

932
00:41:52,970 --> 00:41:55,800
Come hell or high water, we're gonna have this wedding.

933
