 [SIGHS] Oh, man.

943
00:42:31,014 --> 00:42:32,580
 All of us in the band had this dream of going

944
00:42:32,580 --> 00:42:34,830
to Ireland to study the music.

945
00:42:34,830 --> 00:42:36,810
