970
00:43:29,110 --> 00:43:31,020
it is he's in.

971
00:43:31,020 --> 00:43:33,945
 Look, just stop giving Bunny such a bad impression.

972
00:43:33,945 --> 00:43:35,760
Well, I'm sick and tired of you running me down, Ma.

973
00:43:35,760 --> 00:43:36,660
 [CHUCKLES].

974
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:38,080
 Yeah, I know you think it's funny,

975
00:43:38,080 --> 00:43:39,110
but it isn't funny a bit.

976
00:43:41,920 --> 00:43:45,110
 There is something between you two.

977
00:43:45,110 --> 00:43:46,020
 Yeah, I like her.

978
00:43:46,020 --> 00:43:48,180
What of it?

979
00:43:48,180 --> 00:43:52,170
 Remember what I told you, Bunny, just remember.

980
00:43:52,170 --> 00:43:53,220
 Oh, hell, I'm going to bed.

981
00:43:55,770 --> 00:43:56,670
Come on, Bunny.

982
00:43:56,670 --> 00:43:57,620
[SNAPS] Come along now.

983
00:43:57,620 --> 00:43:58,540
 To bed?

984
00:43:58,540 --> 00:43:59,640
 Yeah, it's been a long day.

985
00:43:59,640 --> 00:44:01,260
