989
00:44:07,480 --> 00:44:08,380
Women.

990
00:44:17,652 --> 00:44:18,628
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

991
00:44:18,628 --> 00:44:20,280
Bunny, you need something to wear to bed?

992
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:21,180
 Yes.

993
00:44:26,642 --> 00:44:28,055
WALTER: How about this big old shirt?

994
00:44:28,055 --> 00:44:28,955
 That'll do.

995
00:44:32,770 --> 00:44:34,720
If you like sleeping with the light on.

996
00:44:49,420 --> 00:44:50,420
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

997
00:44:50,420 --> 00:44:51,320
WALTER: Bunny?

998
00:44:51,320 --> 00:44:52,930
Can I come in a second?

999
00:44:52,930 --> 00:44:54,680
 You never bothered asking before.

