00:47:01,280 --> 00:47:02,180
[SCREAMS]

1042
00:47:02,180 --> 00:47:05,160
 Have you got the money, scum?

1043
00:47:05,160 --> 00:47:06,290
- Ah. - No, please!

1044
00:47:06,290 --> 00:47:07,370
He's-- he's going to have money.

